h1. formatNumber 

h2. Purpose

Allows the formatting of numbers using the same patterns defined by the [DecimalFormat|http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4.2/docs/api/java/text/DecimalFormat.html] class.

h2. Examples

{code:xml}
<g:formatNumber number="${myNumber}" format="\\$###,##0" />
{code}

h2. Description

Attributes

* @format@ (required) - The format to use for the number
* @number@ (required) - The number object to formate



